{"tid":2457103,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【元朗7.21】法官裁定所有被告表證成立 「飛天南」明天將自辯","createTime":"2021-03-22T11:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:17:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83d3432d7c106bb6bc75e3661ba521f830e6fb72","tid":2457103,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）前年7月21日元朗站發生白衣人襲擊，8人被控暴動等罪，其中6人不認罪。案件今（22日）第20天續審，法官葉佐文今裁定案中共6名被告的表面證供均成立。被告「飛天南」吳偉南明將自辯，並會傳召3名辯方證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n葉官裁定表證成立，被告「飛天南」吳偉南明將自辯，並會傳召3名辯方證人作供，主要提及被告未到場前曾在哪裏出現，3人作供共需約半小時。而第二被告黃英傑則有機會自辯，其餘被告傾向不自辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081588&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=c1a3d57b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081588&h=344dc2a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081588</a>"},{"pid":"edc1f5558db0e7f7eb8a146f6c1cc98dbaf07619","tid":2457103,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"佢係唔係想話自己好愛國，係為國出頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef245f0208411e8d5a77a61621ff65d6320c84ad","tid":2457103,"uid":5490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7O7j2Z2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7O7j2Z2.png&h=e29dcaf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56ecb012a92fdea0b4774621bf178e59dfb89764","tid":2457103,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"樓主手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}